    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/lac/ret/6041460821.html"></div>
        </div>
Ron Herman is searching for talented Sales Associates to provide an outstanding customer experience in our landmark Fred Segal Melrose location. <br>
<br>
As a Ron Herman Selling Associate, your primary role is to drive sales through developing strong customer relationships, demonstrating an entrepreneurial approach to growing your customer base and partnering successfully with other team members. The Selling Associate is responsible for individual and department store sales goals. Ron Herman Selling Associates must be knowledgeable and passionate about our collections and designers. The ideal candidate understands the importance of building their client base and professional service practices. In addition, the Selling Associate should consistently look for opportunities to exceed their customers' expectations. All Ron Herman employees are expected to act with kindness, enthusiasm and optimism. <br>
<br>
Key Accountabilities:<br>
<br>
Maintain a strong floor presence to drive sales <br>
<br>
Demonstrate excellent customer relations and follow through<br>
<br>
Maintain and build a strong personal client base<br>
<br>
Ensure a positive and harmonious work environment<br>
<br>
Must demonstrate the highest level of professionalism<br>
<br>
Skills Summary:<br>
<br>
A minimum of 1 year of retail sales experience with references<br>
<br>
Strong interpersonal and communication skills<br>
<br>
Must be willing to work in a TEAM ENVIRONMENT.<br>
<br>
*Current client books a huge plus<br>
<br>
<br>
Please send resumes (and cover letter) only - no phone calls please.<br>
<br>
Qualified candidates only. Thank you.<br>
    </section>

